<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(قُتِلَ الْإِنْسَانُ مَا أَكْفَرَهُ (١٧)</span>) .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(مَا أَكْفَرَهُ)</span> : تَعَجُّبٌ؛ أَوِ اسْتِفْهَامٌ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(مِنْ أَيِّ شَيْءٍ خَلَقَهُ (١٨)</span> مِنْ نُطْفَةٍ خَلَقَهُ فَقَدَّرَهُ <span class="c2">(١٩)</span>) .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(مِنْ نُطْفَةٍ)</span> : مُتَعَلِّقٌ بِخَلَقَ الثَّانِيَةِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(ثُمَّ السَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُ (٢٠)</span>) .<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(ثُمَّ السَّبِيلَ)</span> : هُوَ مَفْعُولُ فِعْلٍ مَحْذُوفٍ؛ أَيْ ثُمَّ يَسَّرَ السَّبِيلَ لِلْإِنْسَانِ. وَيَجُوزُ أَنْ يُنْصَبَ بِأَنَّهُ مَفْعُولٌ ثَانٍ لِيَسَّرَهُ. وَالْهَاءُ لِلْإِنْسَانِ؛ أَيْ يَسَّرَهُ السَّبِيلَ؛ أَيْ هُدَاهُ لَهُ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقْضِ مَا أَمَرَهُ (٢٣)</span>) .<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(مَا أَمَرَهُ)</span> : <span class="c2">«مَا»</span> بِمَعْنَى الَّذِي، وَالْعَائِدُ مَحْذُوفٌ؛ أَيْ مَا أَمَرَهُ بِهِ. وَاللَّهُ أَعْلَمُ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(فَلْيَنْظُرِ الْإِنْسَانُ إِلَى طَعَامِهِ (٢٤)</span> أَنَّا صَبَبْنَا <span class="c2">(٢٥)</span>) .<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(أَنَّا صَبَبْنَا)</span> : بِالْكَسْرِ عَلَى الِاسْتِئْنَافِ؛ وَبِالْفَتْحِ عَلَى الْبَدَلِ مِنْ <span class="c2">«طَعَامِهِ»</span> ، أَوْ عَلَى تَقْدِيرِ اللَّامِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c2">(فَإِذَا جَاءَتِ الصَّاخَّةُ (٣٣)</span>) .<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(فَإِذَا جَاءَتِ الصَّاخَّةُ)</span> : مِثْلُ: <span class="c2">«جَاءَتِ الطَّامَّةُ»</span> .<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c5">وَقِيلَ:</span> الْعَامِلُ فِي <span class="c2">«إِذَا»</span> مَعْنَى <span class="c2">«لِكُلِّ امْرِئٍ»</span> وَاللَّهُ أَعْلَمُ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>